name: Trinitaur
description:
Trinitaur. Early experiment in bringing some power and aggression into my visionary psychedelic style. 3d/Photoshop.

Artwork History
- First released in 2015, never minted.
- A section was reproduced as an EP cover by the french psytrance label Sahman Recs for Xside.
- Reinterpreted into a limited run tee shirt for Goa by apparel crew Ultratribe
